BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Neptune conjunction DSC
DESCRIPTION:Transit Neptune (Aries 10°48’) - conjunction - Natal DSC \n \n \nTransit Neptune in Natal 6th house: \nDuring this transit you will be much more prone to stress and psychosomatic health disorders. You will also be more prone to the negative effects of medicines. There may be confusions in your work life, or your work may lead you to charity activities. The influence of Neptune in the 6th house may cause disruptions in your daily routine. A good way to deal with the stress of these disruptions, is doing some spiritual practices, like yoga, meditation, etc. For some individuals, it might be a good period to deal with health issues via hypnosis - quit smoking, address some stress-related and other psychosomatic issues. \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:20301122T151400Z
DTEND:20301122T151400Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165843Z
UID:4_tr_ne_co_ds
END:VEVENT
