BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Neptune conjunction Sun
DESCRIPTION:Transit Neptune (Aries 20°41’) - conjunction - Natal Sun \nYou are more emotionally sensitive, and you have a great imagination. Be careful that somebody does not to hurt your feelings. You are in touch with your intuition, but it might be difficult to keep in touch with your rational side. You can easily lose contact with reality and your practical needs, so you need to be aware of that and do your best to balance the two. \n \nTransit Neptune in Natal 7th house: \nThis transit brings complications to partner relationships. The person you love may seem more distant, or you may be too demanding and expect too much. Their behaviour may be frustrating for you. Try to accept your partner for who he or she is and realize that you cannot control the other person; you should just love him or her unconditionally. If you’re single, you may be attracted to people who will hurt you. It is unlikely that you will meet the right person during this transit, so be careful if you meet a new romantic partner.  In business relationship be aware of misunderstandings, vagueness (in negotiations or contracts) or even deceit. \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
