BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Uranus conjunction MC
DESCRIPTION:Transit Uranus (Cancer 12°27’) - conjunction - Natal MC \n \n \nTransit Uranus in Natal 10th house: \nDuring this transit you will experience a change in your career and relationships with people in authority - parents, bosses etc. You may either discover talent that you didn’t know you had and turn it into a career or take an innovative approach that will bring you recognition in your existing profession. You may also discover a new career path you want to try, or you may long for more freedom at work. This is because in this period you find it hard to take orders. However, be careful that impulsiveness and the desire for freedom does not affect your career.  \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:20360516T222400Z
DTEND:20360516T222400Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165843Z
UID:17_tr_ur_co_mc
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Pluto conjunction Venus
DESCRIPTION:Transit Pluto (Pisces 4°24’) - conjunction - Natal Venus \nYou will expect much more from your relationships than you are getting now. You will be more passionate, and you will long for drama. But be careful not to become obsessed. If you do not have a deep-rooted relationship with someone, you may stop seeing them. This does not only apply to your romantic relationships; it is also true for friendships. On the other hand, you may meet someone who will help you grow personally.  \n \nTransit Pluto in Natal 5th house: \nTransit Pluto in this house will bring aggressiveness or at least less tolerance into your love life. You might want to change your partner’s behaviour that bothers you and you may even use force. You will be more realistic. You should also expect more drama and a greater desire for relationships that will be much more intense and passionate. You may also have the tendency to play games and cause conflicts just to spice up your relationship. If you are single, it is possible that you will enter a relationship that will cause an intense transformation and change your life. If you have children, expect problems caused by their rebellious behaviour. Beware of your tendency towards manipulative behaviour and the tendency to control things around you.  \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:20460324T044400Z
DTEND:20460324T044400Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165843Z
UID:18_tr_pl_co_ve
END:VEVENT
