BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Uranus conjunction Ascendant
DESCRIPTION:Transit Uranus (Libra 10°48’) - conjunction - Natal Ascendant \n \n \nTransit Uranus in Natal 1st house: \nDuring this transit, you will have the need to get out of your comfort zone and express yourself freely. Uranus will bring big changes, and when it passes through the 1st house, these changes will be related to your personality and appearance. You will not be concerned with what others think and expect from you. You will have the need to be independent and you will be open to unconventional experiences. You will also be more willing to take risks and plunge into things without fear. Other people may be surprised by your fearless and rebellious attitude, so you may feel growing distance between you and some people. Beware of impulsive behaviour.  \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:20541011T081100Z
DTEND:20541011T081100Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165843Z
