BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Neptune conjunction Mars
DESCRIPTION:Transit Neptune (Gemini 24°26’) - conjunction - Natal Mars \nThe effect of this transit will increase your potential to attract the things you need into your life or, on the contrary, to attract negative forces. The exact effect depends on the position of Mars in your personal horoscope. You may feel a lack of inspiration and confidence. On the other hand, if you are extroverted, this transit will benefit you and you will be brimming with inspiration.  \n \nTransit Neptune in Natal 9th house: \nYou will have the desire to expand your spirituality. You may be interested in spiritual teachings and metaphysics. You may experience a burst of creativity, which will be especially beneficial for you if you make a living by writing. If you are still studying, you will have difficulty concentrating for long periods of time and you will find it hard to study. You will long to be near water sources. Confusion and misunderstandings associated with travel, legal matters, or university education may occur.  \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:20620731T100600Z
DTEND:20620731T100600Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165843Z
