BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Pluto conjunction Mercury
DESCRIPTION:Transit Pluto (Pisces 28°55’) - conjunction - Natal Mercury \nDuring this period, you will see changes in the way you think. You may decide to go back to school, get involved in a research project, or your work will require understanding large volumes of new information. This information can move you to your destination. You will be determined to find out the whole truth and a shallow explanation will not be enough for you.  \n \nTransit Pluto in Natal 6th house: \nYou should be careful not to sacrifice yourself during this transit. Pluto in this house brings a desire to selflessly help others, but you must not overdo it. It teaches you to overcome pain, disappointment and hypersensitivity. It also teaches you not to be full of yourself and deal with your failures. These processes are necessary to create a new integrated personality. It is a good time to undergo therapy. You should keep to your daily routine and exercise regularly. It is also important that you maintain a healthy diet and try to detoxify and regenerate your body. \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:20660409T212400Z
DTEND:20660409T212400Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165843Z
UID:43_tr_pl_co_me
END:VEVENT
