BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Uranus conjunction Neptune
DESCRIPTION:Transit Uranus (Sagittarius 9°22’) - conjunction - Natal Neptune \nThis transit has a very strong effect on your psyche. If you are not aware of this, it can lead to depression and alcohol or substance abuse. But it can also have a positive effect - the expansion of your consciousness. If you become ill at this time, there may be difficulties with accurate diagnostics of the problem.  \n \nTransit Uranus in Natal 3rd house: \nThanks to this transit, you will experience a period of great mental stimulation and change. You will want to learn new things or start studying a new field. This enthusiasm may not last long, but you will still be looking for a way to express yourself and you will do great especially in writing and public speaking. You will be interested in unusual ideas, disciplines and thoughts. This will open new horizons and help you break free from your daily routine. You may also want to change your look and improve your image.  \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:20670129T021500Z
DTEND:20670129T021500Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165843Z
UID:45_tr_ur_co_ne
END:VEVENT
