BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Uranus conjunction Moon
DESCRIPTION:Transit Uranus (Sagittarius 10°13’) - conjunction - Natal Moon \nThis transit brings unexpected surprises to your home and family affairs. You may lose your home or the possibility to rely on your mother or relatives. You may also experience the feeling of estrangement from the closest person or have complicated relationships with women. These changes will teach you to rely on yourself and be more independent.  \n \nTransit Uranus in Natal 3rd house: \nThanks to this transit, you will experience a period of great mental stimulation and change. You will want to learn new things or start studying a new field. This enthusiasm may not last long, but you will still be looking for a way to express yourself and you will do great especially in writing and public speaking. You will be interested in unusual ideas, disciplines and thoughts. This will open new horizons and help you break free from your daily routine. You may also want to change your look and improve your image.  \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:20671128T013800Z
DTEND:20671128T013800Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165843Z
UID:51_tr_ur_co_mo
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Neptune conjunction MC
DESCRIPTION:Transit Neptune (Cancer 12°27’) - conjunction - Natal MC \n \n \nTransit Neptune in Natal 9th house: \nYou will have the desire to expand your spirituality. You may be interested in spiritual teachings and metaphysics. You may experience a burst of creativity, which will be especially beneficial for you if you make a living by writing. If you are still studying, you will have difficulty concentrating for long periods of time and you will find it hard to study. You will long to be near water sources. Confusion and misunderstandings associated with travel, legal matters, or university education may occur.  \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:20700823T192200Z
DTEND:20700823T192200Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165843Z
UID:52_tr_ne_co_mc
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Neptune conjunction MC
DESCRIPTION:Transit Neptune (Cancer 12°27’) - conjunction - Natal MC \n \n \nTransit Neptune in Natal 10th house: \nNeptune in this house gives you the clarity of where you are going in life. However, it also causes inner uneasiness and confusion. If you are someone who always has a plan and your wellbeing depends on being able to adhere to the plan, you will adapt less well to this transit than someone who is more flexible. Other people may have distorted opinions about you, and they may not be able to see who you really are. Try to show them your true self. You may experience problems with older people.  \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:20701209T105300Z
DTEND:20701209T105300Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165843Z
UID:53_tr_ne_co_mc
END:VEVENT
