BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Uranus conjunction IC
DESCRIPTION:Transit Uranus (Capricorn 12°27’) - conjunction - Natal IC \n \n \nTransit Uranus in Natal 4th house: \nDuring this transit you may experience problems at home in the form of unexpected changes to your plans, the need for repairs or changes in routines. Moving is likely, especially if you have natal or transit Mars in this house. Unexpected changes to your plans will test your patience. You will also rethink relationships with your family and think about what family means to you.  \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:20750128T182700Z
DTEND:20750128T182700Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165843Z
UID:55_tr_ur_co_ic
END:VEVENT
